00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:22.240 align:middle line:90%
to explore the "I am" meaning.

00:00:22.240 --> 00:00:24.880 align:middle line:84%
I was introduced to
the "I Am Discourses"

00:00:24.880 --> 00:00:26.420 align:middle line:90%
