want to show people

00:34:28.400 --> 00:34:31.219 align:middle line:84%
because you're so
beautifully talking

00:34:31.219 --> 00:34:33.310 align:middle line:90%
about relationships here.

00:34:33.310 --> 00:34:36.040 align:middle line:84%
And it changes what we're
talking about a little bit,

00:34:36.040 --> 00:34:39.150 align:middle line:84%
but I want you to see how
what Marianne talks about

00:34:39.150 --> 00:34:41.850 align:middle line:84%
can be brought into the context
of anything in your life.

00:34:41.850 --> 00:34:43.204 align:middle line:90%
Take a look at this.

00:34:43.204 --> 00:34:44.870 align:middle line:84%
>>WILLIAMSON: In "A
Course in Miracles,"

00:34:44.870 --> 00:34:48.100 align:middle line:84%
it talks about how religion and
psychotherapy, at their peak,

00:34:48.100 --> 00:34:50.639 align:middle line:84%
are the same thing
because it all

00:34:50.639 --> 00:34:53.070 align:middle line:84%
has to do with the
healing of the mind.

00:34:53.070 --> 00:34:56.730 align:middle line:84%
And even though, when it comes
to romantic relationships

00:34:56.730 --> 00:35:00.060 align:middle line:84%
and those kinds of attachments
with lovers and mates and all

00:35:00.060 --> 00:35:03.420 align:middle line:84%
that, we tend to get
pretty body oriented,

00:35:03.420 --> 00:35:05.210 align:middle line:84%
the truth of the
matter-- and anybody

00:35:05.210 --> 00:35:10.020 align:middle line:84%
knows this who has had much
experience with relationships.

00:35:10.020 --> 00:35:12.090 align:middle line:90%
So much goes on in the mind.

00:35:12.090 --> 00:35:15.660 align:middle line:84%
So when you heal your mind, you
heal every other relationship.

00:35:15.660 --> 00:35:17.730 align:middle line:84%
And in spiritual
terms, the idea here

00:35:17.730 --> 00:35:21.830 align:middle line:84%
is that when you are at one
with your divine center,

00:35:21.830 --> 00:35:24.040 align:middle line:84%
you will experience
oneness with other people.

00:35:24.040 --> 00:35:26.160 align:middle line:84%
If you take care of that
primary relationship,

00:35:26.160 --> 00:35:28.270 align:middle line:84%
God is your primary
relationship.

00:35:28.270 --> 00:35:30.620 align:middle line:84%
So if you take care of
the primary relationship,

00:35:30.620 --> 00:35:32.740 align:middle line:84%
then you will find
yourself in alignment

00:35:32.740 --> 00:35:34.700 align:middle line:90%
with other human relationships.

00:35:34.700 --> 00:35:37.890 align:middle line:84%
But when you are fractured
in your relationship

00:35:37.890 --> 00:35:40.500 align:middle line:84%
to the divine, you
will find that fracture

00:35:40.500 --> 00:35:43.980 align:middle line:84%
reflected in your
relationships with people.

00:35:43.980 --> 00:35:48.420 align:middle line:84%
So taking care of your
divine relationship

00:35:48.420 --> 00:35:53.270 align:middle line:84%
is taking care of yourself
because your Self,

00:35:53.270 --> 00:35:57.800 align:middle line:84%
with a capital S, is only
found in your oneness with God.

00:35:57.800 --> 00:36:02.300 align:middle line:84%
So if you do not do that,
then you're missing something.

00:36:02.300 --> 00:36:04.190 align:middle line:84%
And you tend to project
on to other people

00:36:04.190 --> 00:36:05.820 align:middle line:90%
that they can give it to you.

00:36:05.820 --> 00:36:08.630 align:middle line:84%
So if you are in
the realm of Self

00:36:08.630 --> 00:36:10.700 align:middle line:84%
with a capital S,
which can only be found

00:36:10.700 --> 00:36:12.640 align:middle line:84%
through your
relationship to God,

00:36:12.640 --> 00:36:16.080 align:middle line:84%
then you saunter out into
the world a whole person,

00:36:16.080 --> 00:36:17.902 align:middle line:84%
and you're not coming
from a wounded place

00:36:17.902 --> 00:36:19.360 align:middle line:84%
where you are
subconsciously trying

00:36:19.360 --> 00:36:21.310 align:middle line:84%
to get somebody else
to complete you,

00:36:21.310 --> 00:36:23.050 align:middle line:84%
trying to get somebody
else to fix you.

00:36:23.050 --> 00:36:24.440 align:middle line:90%
You're completed by God.

00:36:24.440 --> 00:36:29.100 align:middle line:84%
You're completed by something
which is within you.

00:36:29.100 --> 00:36:32.450 align:middle line:84%
And then you don't go out there
with this needy thing going on.

00:36:32.450 --> 00:36:34.880 align:middle line:84%
This energy of will
you come give it to me.

00:36:34.880 --> 00:36:38.490 align:middle line:84%
You go out there
with a sense of being

00:36:38.490 --> 00:36:40.490 align:middle line:84%
a complete human
being who's looking

00:36:40.490 --> 00:36:42.370 align:middle line:84%
for another complete
human being.

00:36:42.370 --> 00:36:45.390 align:middle line:84%
Somebody said to me-- a
woman at one of my seminars.

00:36:45.390 --> 00:36:47.640 align:middle line:84%
Many years ago, she said,
well, the way you're talking

00:36:47.640 --> 00:36:51.360 align:middle line:90%
about it, we wouldn't need men.

00:36:51.360 --> 00:36:51.870 align:middle line:90%
We're whole.

00:36:51.870 --> 00:36:52.440 align:middle line:90%
We're complete.

00:36:52.440 --> 00:36:53.315 align:middle line:90%
We wouldn't need men.

00:36:53.315 --> 00:36:55.640 align:middle line:84%
I said, no, but we
would desire men.

00:36:55.640 --> 00:37:00.740 align:middle line:84%
And, ultimately, a man
experiences need as control.

00:37:00.740 --> 00:37:04.740 align:middle line:84%
A man-- there's a line
that Pat Allen often says.

00:37:04.740 --> 00:37:07.730 align:middle line:84%
"A man produces into
a woman's desire."

00:37:07.730 --> 00:37:10.120 align:middle line:84%
When a woman is truly
complete in herself,

00:37:10.120 --> 00:37:13.120 align:middle line:84%
it's not a false, harsh
sense of independence.

00:37:13.120 --> 00:37:15.070 align:middle line:90%
It's a very surrendered place.

00:37:15.070 --> 00:37:17.660 align:middle line:84%
A person who knows how
to surrender to God

00:37:17.660 --> 00:37:22.010 align:middle line:84%
has surrender as one of
the notes they can play.

00:37:22.010 --> 00:37:24.780 align:middle line:84%
So a woman who is
truly independent

00:37:24.780 --> 00:37:26.870 align:middle line:84%
is not independent
in the universe.

00:37:26.870 --> 00:37:29.080 align:middle line:84%
She's independent
of other people.

00:37:29.080 --> 00:37:31.920 align:middle line:84%
But she is very
dependent on her creator.

00:37:31.920 --> 00:37:33.300 align:middle line:90%
She's very dependent.

00:37:33.300 --> 00:37:34.690 align:middle line:90%
It makes us very pliable.

00:37:34.690 --> 00:37:36.500 align:middle line:90%
It makes us very surrendered.

00:37:36.500 --> 00:37:40.390 align:middle line:84%
But we're not looking to a
man to be the source of that.

00:37:40.390 --> 00:37:43.520 align:middle line:84%
So when a woman has her
spiritual connection together,

00:37:43.520 --> 00:37:45.540 align:middle line:84%
then the way she is with
any other human being

00:37:45.540 --> 00:37:47.560 align:middle line:90%
is independent within herself.

00:37:47.560 --> 00:37:50.630 align:middle line:84%
But in the right place,
with a trustable man,

00:37:50.630 --> 00:37:53.289 align:middle line:84%
with a man who is
worthy of the job,

00:37:53.289 --> 00:37:55.330 align:middle line:84%
with a man who is strong
enough, with a man who's

00:37:55.330 --> 00:37:58.915 align:middle line:84%
committed enough, with a man
who is worthy of the assignment

00:37:58.915 --> 00:37:59.864 align:middle line:90%
as it were.

